Spread-Client
==========================

Perl implementation of a Spread Toolkit client.  It allows asynchronous
operations for everything EXCEPT connects.

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

See Makefile.PL

